<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{sheriff}
<P>__{(a pause, then calmly)}
<D>__{norman bates' mother has been dead and buried in greenlawn cemetery for the last ten years!}
<A>__{there is a long silence. sam and lila stare at the sheriff.}
