<D>__{it ain't only local history, sam, it's the only murder and suicide case in fairvale ledgers! mrs. bates poisoned this guy she was... involved with, when she found out he was married, then took a helping of the same stuff herself. strychnine. ugly way to die.}
<C>__{mrs. chambers}
<D>__{norman found them dead together. in bed.}
